                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030112-48-defend296 t18030112-48-punish264"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
